<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>ثم رأيته فيه <span class="c2">(٨/٤٨٤)</span> ،<span class="c5"> وقال:</span> <span class="c1">" ربما خالف "</span>.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>